# Design System - InsightHouse

This document defines the complete design system standards for the InsightHouse project. All components, layouts, and styling must follow these guidelines.

## Typography

### Font Family
- **Primary Font**: Geist Sans (applied globally via `layout.tsx`)
- Applied to `<html>` element: `className={GeistSans.className}`
- All text inherits Geist Sans automatically

### Font Sizes
- **Hero Titles**: `text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl` (auth pages), `text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl` (homepage)
- **Section Titles**: `text-3xl md:text-4xl`
- **Card Titles**: `text-lg` or `text-xl`
- **Body Text**: `text-base md:text-lg`
- **Small Text**: `text-sm` or `text-xs`
- **Subtitles**: `text-xl md:text-2xl` (homepage), `text-base md:text-lg` (auth pages)

### Font Weights
- **Bold**: `font-bold` (headings)
- **Semibold**: `font-semibold` (subheadings, card titles)
- **Medium**: `font-medium` (labels, buttons)
- **Light**: `font-light` (descriptions, subtitles)

### Text Effects
- **Gradient Text**: `bg-gradient-to-r from-foreground to-muted-foreground bg-clip-text text-transparent`
- Use for main titles and hero headings

## Colors

### Color System
All colors use HSL variables defined in `globals.css`. Always use semantic color names, never hardcode values.

### Primary Colors
- **Background**: `bg-background` (white in light, very dark in dark)
- **Foreground**: `bg-foreground` (dark in light, light in dark)
- **Card**: `bg-card` (white in light, dark in dark)
- **Primary**: `bg-primary` (dark in light, light in dark)
- **Secondary**: `bg-secondary` (light gray in light, dark gray in dark)
- **Muted**: `bg-muted` (light gray in light, dark gray in dark)
- **Accent**: `bg-accent` (light gray in light, dark gray in dark)

### Form Colors
- **Form Background**: `bg-sidebar-accent` (light gray: #fafafa equivalent)
- **Input Background**: `bg-card` (white: `0 0% 100%`)
- **Input Border**: `border-border/40` (subtle border)

### Gradients
- **Auth Pages (Light Mode)**: `bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary via-card/80 to-accent/60`
- **Auth Pages (Dark Mode)**: `bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary via-secondary/95 to-secondary/90`
- **Hero Sections**: Use gradient backgrounds for visual interest

### Borders
- **Default Border**: `border-border/50` (light mode), `border-border/30` (dark mode)
- **Subtle Border**: `border-border/40` (inputs, cards)
- **Strong Border**: `border-border` (dividers, containers)

## Components

### Button Component (`@/lib/components/ui/button.tsx`)

#### Variants
- **`default`**: Standard button with primary background
- **`primary-rounded`**: Rounded full button with foreground background, includes hover lift effect
- **`outline-rounded`**: Rounded full button with transparent background and border
- **`outline-primary`**: Rounded full button with border, hover fills with primary
- **`destructive`**: Red button for destructive actions
- **`secondary`**: Secondary background button
- **`ghost`**: Transparent button with hover background
- **`link`**: Text link style

#### Sizes
- **`default`**: `h-9 px-4 py-2`
- **`sm`**: `h-8 px-3 text-xs`
- **`lg`**: `h-10 px-8`
- **`lg-rounded`**: `h-10 px-5 xs:px-6` (for rounded buttons)
- **`icon`**: `h-9 w-9`

#### Hover Effects
All rounded buttons include:
- `hover:-translate-y-0.5` (lift effect)
- `active:translate-y-0 active:scale-[0.98]` (press effect)
- `hover:shadow-md` (for primary-rounded)

#### Usage
```tsx
<Button variant="primary-rounded" size="lg-rounded">
  Action
</Button>
```

### Input Component (`@/lib/components/ui/input.tsx`)

#### Base Styles
- **Height**: `h-11 md:h-12` (responsive)
- **Background**: `bg-card` (white)
- **Border**: `border border-border/40`
- **Border Radius**: `rounded-lg`
- **Text Size**: `text-sm`
- **Padding**: `px-3 py-1`
- **Placeholder**: `placeholder:text-muted-foreground/50`
- **Transitions**: `transition-all`

#### Focus States
- **Border**: `focus:border-primary/50`
- **Ring**: `focus:ring-1 focus:ring-primary/20`
- **Outline**: `focus:outline-none`

#### Usage
```tsx
<Input
  id="email"
  placeholder="seu@email.com"
  type="email"
  value={email}
  onChange={(e) => setEmail(e.target.value)}
/>
```

### Card Component
- **Background**: `bg-card` or `bg-card/50` (with transparency)
- **Border**: `border-0` (no border by default) or `border border-border/40`
- **Shadow**: `shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg` (with hover effect)
- **Backdrop Blur**: `backdrop-blur-sm` (for glassmorphism effect)

## Layout Patterns

### Authentication Pages Layout

#### Two-Column Grid
- **Container**: `grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2`
- **Full Height**: `h-screen lg:h-screen`
- **Column Separation**:
  - Information column: `border-r border-border/50 dark:border-border/30`
  - Form column: `border-l border-border/30 dark:border-border/20`

#### Information Column
- **Background Gradient (Light)**: `bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary via-card/80 to-accent/60`
- **Background Gradient (Dark)**: `bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary via-secondary/95 to-secondary/90`
- **Content Layout**: Grid 2 columns with title/subtitle on left, image on right
- **Padding**: `p-12`
- **Text Color**: `text-foreground`

#### Form Column
- **Background**: `bg-sidebar-accent` (#fafafa equivalent)
- **Padding**: `p-6 lg:p-12`
- **Centered Content**: `flex items-center justify-center`

#### Title and Image Layout
- **Grid**: `grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-center`
- **Title Size**: `text-3xl md:text-4xl`
- **Subtitle Size**: `text-sm md:text-base`
- **Image**: `aspect-square` with `max-w-xl` or full width in grid

### Homepage Hero Section
- **Container**: `min-h-screen flex items-center`
- **Grid**: `grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4 lg:gap-6`
- **Text Alignment**: `text-center lg:text-left`
- **Image**: `aspect-square` with responsive sizing

## Spacing

### Standard Spacing Scale
- **Tight**: `space-y-2` or `gap-2`
- **Small**: `space-y-3` or `gap-3`
- **Medium**: `space-y-4` or `gap-4`
- **Large**: `space-y-6` or `gap-6`
- **Extra Large**: `space-y-8` or `gap-8`

### Padding
- **Cards**: `p-4` to `p-6`
- **Sections**: `p-6 lg:p-12`
- **Containers**: `px-6` (horizontal), `py-8` to `py-24` (vertical)

### Margins
- **Between Sections**: `mb-16` or `mb-24`
- **Between Elements**: `mb-4` to `mb-8`
- **Top Spacing**: `mt-8` for images after text

## Borders and Radius

### Border Radius
- **Default**: `rounded-lg` (1rem)
- **Rounded Full**: `rounded-full` (for buttons, badges)
- **Small**: `rounded-md` or `rounded-sm`
- **Large**: `rounded-xl` or `rounded-2xl`

### Borders
- **Subtle**: `border-border/40` or `border-border/30`
- **Medium**: `border-border/50`
- **Strong**: `border-border`

## Shadows

### Box Shadows
- **Small**: `shadow-sm`
- **Medium**: `shadow-md`
- **Large**: `shadow-lg`
- **Hover**: `hover:shadow-lg` or `hover:shadow-xl`

### Custom Shadows
- **Layer Shadows**: `shadow-layer-1` to `shadow-layer-5` (for depth)
- **Inner Shadows**: `shadow-inner-1` to `shadow-inner-5` (for recessed effect)

## Transitions and Animations

### Standard Transitions
- **All Properties**: `transition-all duration-200 ease-out`
- **Transform Only**: `transition-transform duration-200`
- **Colors**: `transition-colors`

### Hover Effects
- **Scale**: `hover:scale-105` (cards, buttons)
- **Lift**: `hover:-translate-y-0.5` (buttons)
- **Press**: `active:translate-y-0 active:scale-[0.98]` (buttons)
- **Shadow**: `hover:shadow-md` or `hover:shadow-lg`

### Icon Animations
- **Scale on Hover**: `group-hover:scale-110` (within group)
- **Color Change**: `group-hover:text-primary transition-colors`

## Illustrations

### SVG Handling
- **Import**: Use direct imports from `@/assets/illustrations/`
- **Dark Mode**: Apply `dark:invert` class for white lines in dark mode
- **Light Mode**: SVGs display with black lines by default
- **Container**: Use `aspect-square` or `aspect-video` for consistent sizing
- **Object Fit**: `object-contain` to preserve aspect ratio

### Illustration Locations
- **Homepage Hero**: `@/assets/illustrations/heroImage.svg`
- **Auth Login**: `@/assets/illustrations/auth/welcomeBack.svg`
- **Auth Register**: `@/assets/illustrations/auth/sales.svg`
- **Feature Cards**: Various SVGs from `@/assets/illustrations/`

### Usage Pattern
```tsx
import illustration from '@/assets/illustrations/path/to/illustration.svg'

<Image
  src={illustration}
  alt="Description"
  fill
  className="object-contain dark:invert"
/>
```

## Responsive Design

### Breakpoints
- **Mobile**: Default (no prefix)
- **Small**: `sm:` (640px+)
- **Medium**: `md:` (768px+)
- **Large**: `lg:` (1024px+)
- **Extra Large**: `xl:` (1280px+)

### Common Patterns
- **Hide on Mobile**: `hidden lg:flex`
- **Stack on Mobile**: `flex-col lg:flex-row`
- **Responsive Text**: `text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl`
- **Responsive Spacing**: `gap-4 lg:gap-6`
- **Responsive Padding**: `p-6 lg:p-12`

## Dark Mode

### Color Adaptation
- Always use semantic color variables (never hardcode)
- Colors automatically adapt via CSS variables
- Test components in both modes

### SVG Adaptation
- Apply `dark:invert` to SVGs for proper contrast
- Light mode: black lines
- Dark mode: white lines (via invert)

### Border Adaptation
- Light mode: `border-border/50`
- Dark mode: `border-border/30` (more subtle)

## Form Patterns

### Form Layout
- **Container**: `bg-sidebar-accent` (light gray background)
- **Card**: `bg-transparent border-0` (no card background, transparent)
- **Inputs**: White background (`bg-card`) against gray form background
- **Labels**: `text-xs xs:text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground`
- **Spacing**: `space-y-4 xs:space-y-5 md:space-y-6`

### Form Sections
- **Two-Column Inputs**: `grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 xs:gap-5`
- **Button Row**: `flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-3`
- **Privacy Text**: `text-[10px] xs:text-xs text-muted-foreground/70`

## Card Patterns

### Feature Cards
- **Hover Effect**: `hover:scale-105` with `transition-all duration-300`
- **Shadow**: `shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg`
- **Group Hover**: Use `group` class for coordinated hover effects
- **Icon Container**: `bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary/5`
- **Icon Hover**: `group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform`

### Information Cards
- **Background**: `bg-card/50 backdrop-blur-sm`
- **Border**: `border-0` (no border)
- **Hover**: `hover:scale-[1.02]` (subtle scale)

## Best Practices

### Do's
✅ Always use semantic color variables
✅ Apply consistent spacing using Tailwind scale
✅ Use responsive classes for all layouts
✅ Test components in both light and dark modes
✅ Apply transitions to interactive elements
✅ Use `group` for coordinated hover effects
✅ Import illustrations directly, don't use URLs
✅ Apply `dark:invert` to SVGs for dark mode

### Don'ts
❌ Don't hardcode color values
❌ Don't use inline styles
❌ Don't skip responsive design
❌ Don't forget dark mode testing
❌ Don't use external image URLs for illustrations
❌ Don't create custom components when shadcn/ui variants exist
❌ Don't mix different transition patterns

## Component Consistency

### All UI Components Must:
1. Use semantic color variables
2. Support dark mode automatically
3. Include proper focus states
4. Have consistent spacing
5. Use standard border radius
6. Include appropriate transitions
7. Be responsive by default

