When refactoring dashboard components:
- [ ] Replace custom buttons with Button component variants
- [ ] Replace custom inputs with Input component
- [ ] Use semantic colors, not hardcoded values
- [ ] Apply consistent spacing scale
- [ ] Add hover effects where appropriate
- [ ] Ensure dark mode compatibility
- [ ] Test responsive behavior
- [ ] Use Card component for containers
- [ ] Apply consistent border radius
- [ ] Include proper transitions

